{"tid":1242520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請支持「HKU反送中關注組」6月19日太子站C出口反送中街站","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:49:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7486205e36f0b5d945f15449f2f4aa6cf9b47a52","tid":1242520,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/LXcgGh9C/HKU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FLXcgGh9C%2FHKU.png&h=1d58a6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKUAntiExtraditionBillConcernGroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKUAntiExtraditionBillConcernGroup&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8daCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=dc72ef29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKUAntiExtraditionBillConcernGroup</a><br />\n【六月十九日反送中街站詳情】<br />\n<br />\n政府至今仍然未答應我哋嘅訴求，如果政府聽日（20號）下午五點之前仍未回應，希望大家應學界呼籲支持不合作運動，並於星期五到政府總部以和平方式要求政府直接回應。我哋會繼續落區宣傳，提醒各位市民切勿鬆懈，要逼使政府撤回惡法、撤控義士以及追究警察濫暴。香港大學反送中關注組今日亦會擺設街站，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：六月十九日（三）<br />\n時間：晚上六時至九時 <br />\n地點：太子站C出口<br />\n<br />\n屆時亦會同時進行「TVB唔俾你睇嘅真相」放映會，有興趣幫手嘅同學可以聯絡關注組或者直接去到上述地點幫手，謝謝。"},{"pid":"5c22311dee9910fe1346b04c2a70fbbb4d5210be","tid":1242520,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請大家支持下後生仔啦<br />\n<br />\n放工後到場支持, 要人多<br />\n<br />\n黑警可能會蝦學生, 一齊去保護學生"},{"pid":"4f84f6fcf90e04cd15ac7775b7c5349e0f56dfac","tid":1242520,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc2a876b5fa7e6bc2bb1505c50e80fd129a1bd3","tid":1242520,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議，認同請幫手推post：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bc94bbde3c13e318515298589571a694266641","tid":1242520,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}